    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support the development of technical architecture designs and documentation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Assist in technical options analysis and technology evaluation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Help design technical solutions and software architectures</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Contribute to technical design reviews and code quality assessments</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support technical delivery and development activities</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Assist with technical testing and performance optimization</li>
    </ul>
</section>

